---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout>
  <article class="py-16">
    <a href="/#work" class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-zinc-400 transition hover:text-white">
      <span data-lang="es">Volver</span>
      <span data-lang="en">Back</span>
    </a>

    <div class="mt-6 grid gap-10 md:grid-cols-12">
      <div class="md:col-span-8">
        <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-zinc-500">Case Study</p>
        <h1 class="mt-4 text-4xl font-display md:text-6xl">
          SmartAgro - Cuaderno de Campo
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl text-zinc-300">
          <span data-lang="es">
            Plataforma agricola con trazabilidad, sensores y paneles para operaciones en campo.
          </span>
          <span data-lang="en">
            Agriculture platform with traceability, sensors, and dashboards for field operations.
          </span>
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="md:col-span-4">
        <div class="rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/4 p-6 transition-transform duration-300 ease-out hover:scale-[1.02]">
          <div class="space-y-4 text-sm text-zinc-300">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-zinc-500">
              <span data-lang="es">Rol</span>
              <span data-lang="en">Role</span>
              <span class="text-zinc-300">Full-Stack</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-zinc-500">
              <span>Stack</span>
              <span class="text-zinc-300">React - Flask - MySQL</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-zinc-500">
              <span data-lang="es">Datos</span>
              <span data-lang="en">Data</span>
              <span class="text-zinc-300">LoRaWAN - Influx</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <section class="mt-14 grid gap-10 md:grid-cols-12">
      <div class="md:col-span-4">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-display">El problema</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="md:col-span-8 text-zinc-300">
        <p data-lang="es">
          La operacion diaria estaba fragmentada: cuaderno de campo, sensores y cumplimiento en
          sistemas distintos. Hacia falta una vista unica y confiable.
        </p>
        <p data-lang="en">
          Daily operations were fragmented: field notebook, sensors, and compliance lived in
          different systems. A single reliable view was needed.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-10 grid gap-10 md:grid-cols-12">
      <div class="md:col-span-4">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-display">La solucion</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="md:col-span-8 text-zinc-300">
        <p data-lang="es">
          Backend modular, paneles por rol y dashboards para decisiones rapidas. Todo conectado con
          sensores y trazabilidad normativa.
        </p>
        <p data-lang="en">
          Modular backend, role-based dashboards, and fast decision support. Fully connected to
          sensors and compliance traceability.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-10 grid gap-10 md:grid-cols-12">
      <div class="md:col-span-4">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-display">Arquitectura</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="md:col-span-8 text-zinc-300">
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
          <li>- Ingesta IoT (LoRaWAN/ChirpStack) a series temporales.</li>
          <li>- API modular para cuaderno, explotaciones y tratamientos.</li>
          <li>- Frontend React para operacion en campo y reporting.</li>
          <li>- Observabilidad basica para calidad de datos.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
